[{"id": 583460, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3661, "text": "Hamd, g\u00f6kleri ve yeri yaratan, melekleri iki\u015fer, \u00fc\u00e7er, d\u00f6rder kanatl\u0131 el\u00e7iler k\u0131lan Allah'a mahsustur. O, yaratmada diledi\u011fi kadar art\u0131r\u0131r. Ger\u00e7ekten Allah her \u015feye k\u00e2dirdir."}, {"id": 583461, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3662, "text": "Allah, insanlara rahmetinden neyi a\u00e7arsa art\u0131k onu tutacak, k\u0131sacak olan yoktur. Her neyi de tutar k\u0131sarsa, onu da, ondan sonra salacak yoktur. O, \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fcd\u00fcr, h\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibidir."}, {"id": 583462, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3663, "text": "Ey insanlar! Allah'\u0131n \u00fczerinizdeki nimetini an\u0131n. Allah'tan ba\u015fka bir yarat\u0131c\u0131 m\u0131 var? O size g\u00f6kten ve yerden r\u0131z\u0131k verir. O'ndan ba\u015fka il\u00e2h yoktur. O halde (haktan) nas\u0131l \u00e7evrilirsiniz?"}, {"id": 583463, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3664, "text": "E\u011fer onlar seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, senden \u00f6nce bir\u00e7ok peygamberler de yalanland\u0131lar. B\u00fct\u00fcn i\u015fler Allah'a d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcl\u00fcr."}, {"id": 583464, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3665, "text": "Ey insanlar! Haberiniz olsun ki, Allah'\u0131n vaadi muhakkak hakt\u0131r. Sak\u0131n bu d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131 sizi aldatmas\u0131n, sak\u0131n o aldat\u0131c\u0131 \u015feytan sizi, Allah hakk\u0131nda da aldatmas\u0131n."}, {"id": 583465, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3666, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc \u015feytan size d\u00fc\u015fmand\u0131r. Siz de onu d\u00fc\u015fman tutun. O etraf\u0131na toplanan taraftarlar\u0131n\u0131 ancak cehennemliklerden olsunlar diye davet eder."}, {"id": 583466, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3667, "text": "\u0130nk\u00e2r edenler i\u00e7in \u015fiddetli bir azab vard\u0131r. \u0130man edip salih amel i\u015fleyenler i\u00e7in de bir ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma ve b\u00fcy\u00fck bir m\u00fckafat vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 583467, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3668, "text": "Ya k\u00f6t\u00fc ameli kendisine allanm\u0131\u015f pullanm\u0131\u015f da onu g\u00fczel g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f olan kimse de mi (iman edip salih amel i\u015fleyenler gibi olacak)? \u015e\u00fcphe yok ki Allah diledi\u011fini \u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131r, diledi\u011fini de do\u011fru yola \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131r. O halde can\u0131n onlara kar\u015f\u0131 hasretlerle (\u00fcz\u00fcnt\u00fclerle) s\u0131k\u0131l\u0131p gitmesin. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Allah, onlar\u0131n b\u00fct\u00fcn yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 bilir."}, {"id": 583468, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3669, "text": "R\u00fczg\u00e2rlar\u0131 g\u00f6nderip bir bulut kald\u0131ran da Allah't\u0131r. Derken biz o (bulutu) \u00f6lm\u00fc\u015f bir beldeye sevketmi\u015fizdir. B\u00f6ylece yery\u00fcz\u00fcne \u00f6lm\u00fcnden sonra onunla hayat veririz. \u0130\u015fte o dirilme de b\u00f6yledir."}, {"id": 583469, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3670, "text": "Her kim izzet istiyorsa bilsin ki izzet tamam\u0131yla Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r. O'na ho\u015f kelimeler y\u00fckselir, onu da salih amel y\u00fckseltir. K\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fckler kuranlara gelince, onlara \u015fiddetli bir azab vard\u0131r. Onlar\u0131n tuzaklar\u0131 hep darmada\u011f\u0131n olur."}, {"id": 583470, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3671, "text": "Hem Allah sizi bir topraktan, sonra bir damla sudan yaratt\u0131. Sonra sizi \u00e7iftler k\u0131ld\u0131. O'nun bilgisi olmadan ne bir di\u015fi hamile olur, ne do\u011furur. Kendisine \u00f6m\u00fcr verilenin de \u00f6mr\u00fcn\u00fcn uzat\u0131lmas\u0131 da, \u00f6mr\u00fcnden k\u0131salt\u0131lmas\u0131 da mutlaka bir kitapta yaz\u0131l\u0131d\u0131r. \u015e\u00fcphe yok ki bu, Allah'a g\u00f6re kolayd\u0131r."}, {"id": 583471, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3672, "text": "Hem iki deniz e\u015fit olmuyor. \u015eu tatl\u0131, hararet keser, i\u00e7erken (bo\u011fazdan) kayar; \u015fu da tuzlu, yakar kavurur. Bununla beraber her birinden taze bir et yersiniz ve bir ziynet \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131r, giyinirsiniz. Allah'\u0131n l\u00fctfundan nasib arayas\u0131n\u0131z diye suyu yara yara giden gemileri de g\u00f6r\u00fcrs\u00fcn. Gerek ki \u015f\u00fckredeceksiniz."}, {"id": 583472, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3673, "text": "O, geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcze sokuyor, g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fc de geceye sokuyor. G\u00fcne\u015fi ve ay\u0131 emrine \u00e2m\u00e2de k\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Her biri mukadder bir gayeye ak\u0131p gidiyor. \u0130\u015fte bu g\u00f6rd\u00fcklerinizi yapan Allah sizin Rabbinizdir. M\u00fclk (h\u00fck\u00fcmranl\u0131k) O'nundur. O'ndan ba\u015fka tapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z ise, bir \u00e7ekirdek zar\u0131n\u0131 bile idare edemezler."}, {"id": 583473, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3674, "text": "Kendilerine dua ederseniz duan\u0131z\u0131 i\u015fitmezler. \u0130\u015fitseler bile size cevab\u0131n\u0131 veremezler. K\u0131yamet g\u00fcn\u00fc de kendilerini Allah'a ortak ko\u015ftu\u011funuzu ink\u00e2r ederler. Sana her \u015feyden haberdar olan (Allah) gibi bir haber veren olmaz."}, {"id": 583474, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3675, "text": "Ey insanlar! Siz Allah'a muhta\u00e7s\u0131n\u0131z. Allah ise zengin ve her hamde l\u00e2y\u0131kt\u0131r."}, {"id": 583475, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3676, "text": "E\u011fer O dilerse sizi yok eder ve yerinize yeni bir halk getirir."}, {"id": 583476, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3677, "text": "Ve bu, Allah'a g\u00f6re zor bir \u015fey de\u011fildir."}, {"id": 583477, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3678, "text": "Hem g\u00fcnah \u00e7eken bir kimse, ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131n g\u00fcnah\u0131n\u0131 \u00e7ekmeyecek; y\u00fck\u00fc a\u011f\u0131r basan, onun y\u00fcklenilmesine \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rsa da ondan bir \u015fey y\u00fcklenilmeyecek, isterse bir yak\u0131n\u0131 olsun. Fakat sen ancak o kimseleri sak\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131s\u0131n ki, gaybda Rablerinin korkusunu duyarlar, namaz\u0131 d\u00fcr\u00fcst k\u0131larlar. Temizlenen de s\u0131rf kendisi i\u00e7in temizlenir. Nihayet d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f Allah'ad\u0131r."}, {"id": 583478, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3679, "text": "Ne k\u00f6r ile g\u00f6ren e\u015fit olur,"}, {"id": 583479, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3680, "text": "Ne de karanl\u0131klar ile ayd\u0131nl\u0131k,"}, {"id": 583480, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3681, "text": "Ve ne de g\u00f6lge ile s\u0131cakl\u0131k."}, {"id": 583481, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3682, "text": "\u00d6l\u00fclerle diriler de e\u015fit olmaz. Ger\u00e7i Allah, her diledi\u011fine i\u015fittirirse de sen, kabirlerdekine i\u015fittirecek de\u011filsin."}, {"id": 583482, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3683, "text": "Sen sadece bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n."}, {"id": 583483, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3684, "text": "Muhakkak ki biz seni hak ile hem bir m\u00fcjdeci, hem bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 olarak g\u00f6nderdik. Hi\u00e7bir \u00fcmmet de yoktur ki, i\u00e7lerinde bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 ge\u00e7mi\u015f olmas\u0131n."}, {"id": 583484, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3685, "text": "Seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, onlardan \u00f6ncekiler de yalanlam\u0131\u015flard\u0131. Onlara peygamberleri mucizelerle, sahifelerle ve ayd\u0131nlat\u0131c\u0131 kitaplarla gelmi\u015flerdi."}, {"id": 583485, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3686, "text": "Sonra ben o ink\u00e2r edenleri tutup yakalad\u0131m. O zaman beni ink\u00e2r etmek nas\u0131l oldu?"}, {"id": 583486, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3687, "text": "G\u00f6rmedin mi Allah g\u00f6kten bir su indirdi. Biz onunla renkleri ba\u015fka ba\u015fka meyveler \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131k. Da\u011flarda da yollar, beyazl\u0131 k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131l\u0131 \u00e7e\u015fitli renklerde ve kapkara topraklar var."}, {"id": 583487, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3688, "text": "Yine insanlardan, hayvanlardan ve davarlardan da t\u00fcrl\u00fc renklileri vard\u0131r. Kullar\u0131 i\u00e7inde Allah'tan ancak \u00e2limler korkar. \u015e\u00fcphe yok ki Allah \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fcd\u00fcr. H\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibidir."}, {"id": 583488, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3689, "text": "Allah'\u0131n kitab\u0131n\u0131 okuyan, namaz\u0131 k\u0131lan ve kendilerine verdi\u011fimiz r\u0131z\u0131ktan gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k olarak verenler, kesinlikle batma ihtimali olmayan bir ticaret umarlar."}, {"id": 583489, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3690, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Allah m\u00fckafatlar\u0131n\u0131 kendilerine tamamen \u00f6dedikten ba\u015fka, l\u00fctfundan onlara fazlas\u0131n\u0131 da verecektir. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc O \u00e7ok ba\u011f\u0131\u015flay\u0131c\u0131 ve \u015f\u00fckr\u00fcn kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 vericidir."}, {"id": 583490, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3691, "text": "Kitaplar i\u00e7inde sana vahyetti\u011fimiz kitap da kendinden \u00f6ncekileri tasdik edici olmak \u00fczere bir hakt\u0131r. \u015e\u00fcphe yok ki, Allah, kullar\u0131n\u0131n b\u00fct\u00fcn hallerinden haberdard\u0131r ve her \u015feyi g\u00f6rendir."}, {"id": 583491, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3692, "text": "Sonra biz o kitab\u0131 kullar\u0131m\u0131zdan s\u00fcz\u00fcp se\u00e7tiklerimize miras b\u0131rakt\u0131k. Onlardan da nefislerine zulmeden var, orta yolu tutan var, Allah'\u0131n izniyle hay\u0131rlarda ileri ge\u00e7enler var. \u0130\u015fte bu b\u00fcy\u00fck l\u00fctuftur."}, {"id": 583492, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3693, "text": "Onlara Adn cennetleri vard\u0131r. Onlar oraya gireceklerdir. Orada alt\u0131n bilezikler ve incilerle s\u00fcsleneceklerdir. Orada elbiseleri de ipektir."}, {"id": 583493, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3694, "text": "Onlar orada \u015f\u00f6yle derler: \"Hamd olsun Allah'a, bizden o \u00fcz\u00fcnt\u00fcy\u00fc giderdi. Ger\u00e7ekten Rabbimiz \u00e7ok ba\u011f\u0131\u015flay\u0131c\u0131 ve \u015f\u00fckr\u00fcn kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 vericidir.\""}, {"id": 583494, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3695, "text": "\"L\u00fctfundan bizi durulacak bir yurda kondurdu. Burada bize yorgunluk gelmeyecek, burada bize usan\u00e7 gelmeyecektir.\""}, {"id": 583495, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3696, "text": "\u0130nk\u00e2r edenlere gelince, onlara cehennem ate\u015fi vard\u0131r. H\u00fck\u00fcm verilmez ki \u00f6ls\u00fcnler, kendilerinden biraz azab da hafifletilmez. \u0130\u015fte biz her nank\u00f6r\u00fc b\u00f6yle cezaland\u0131r\u0131r\u0131z."}, {"id": 583496, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3697, "text": "Onlar, orada \u015f\u00f6yle feryad ederler: \"Ey Rabbimiz! Bizleri \u00e7\u0131kar, yapageldiklerimizden ba\u015fka salih bir amel yapal\u0131m.\" (Onlara): \"Size d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnecek olan\u0131n d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnece\u011fi kadar bir \u00f6m\u00fcr vermedik mi? Hem size uyar\u0131c\u0131 da gelmi\u015fti. O halde azab\u0131 tad\u0131n. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc zalimleri kurtaracak yoktur.\" (denir)."}, {"id": 583497, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3698, "text": "\u015e\u00fcphe yok ki Allah, g\u00f6klerin ve yerin gayb\u0131n\u0131 bilir. Elbette o, sinelerin i\u00e7inde olanlar\u0131 da bilir."}, {"id": 583498, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3699, "text": "Sizi yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde halifeler yapan O'dur. Art\u0131k kim k\u00fcfrederse, k\u00fcfr\u00fc kendi aleyhinedir. K\u00e2firlerin k\u00fcf\u00fcrleri, Rablerinin kat\u0131nda kendilerine bu\u011fzdan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey art\u0131rmaz, k\u00e2firlerin k\u00fcf\u00fcrleri kendilerine zarardan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey art\u0131rmaz."}, {"id": 583499, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3700, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz ya, Allah'\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131p da tapmakta oldu\u011funuz ortaklar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131! G\u00f6sterin bana, yer y\u00fcz\u00fcnden neyi yaratm\u0131\u015flard\u0131r?\" Yoksa onlar\u0131n g\u00f6k y\u00fcz\u00fcnde bir ortakl\u0131\u011f\u0131 m\u0131 var? Yoksa biz kendilerine bir kitap vermi\u015fiz de ondan bir delil \u00fczerinde mi bulunuyorlar? Hay\u0131r o zalimler, birbirlerine aldatmadan ba\u015fka bir vaadde bulunmuyorlar."}, {"id": 583500, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3701, "text": "Do\u011frusu g\u00f6kleri ve yeri yok oluvermekten, Allah tutuyor. Andolsun ki e\u011fer yok oluverirlerse, onlar\u0131 O'ndan ba\u015fka kimse tutamaz. Ger\u00e7ekten O, \u00e7ok yumu\u015fak davran\u0131r, \u00e7ok ba\u011f\u0131\u015flay\u0131c\u0131d\u0131r."}, {"id": 583501, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3702, "text": "Olanca g\u00fc\u00e7leriyle Allah'a yemin etmi\u015flerdi ki, kendilerine uyar\u0131c\u0131 bir peygamber gelirse, mutlaka ilerideki \u00fcmmetlerin herhagi birinden daha do\u011fru yolda olacaklard\u0131. Fakat kendilerine uyar\u0131c\u0131 bir peygamber geldi\u011fi zaman bu, onlar\u0131n s\u0131rf \u00fcrk\u00fcnt\u00fcleriniart\u0131rd\u0131."}, {"id": 583502, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3703, "text": "(Bu da) yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bir kibirlenme ve bir suikast d\u00fczenidir. Halbuki fena d\u00fczen ancak sahibinin ba\u015f\u0131na ge\u00e7er. O halde \u00f6ncekilerin kanunundan ba\u015fka ne g\u00f6zetiyorlar? Sen Allah'\u0131n s\u00fcnnetinde asla bir de\u011fi\u015fme bulamazs\u0131n. Sen Allah'\u0131n s\u00fcnnetinde asla bir ba\u015fkala\u015fma da bulamazs\u0131n."}, {"id": 583503, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3704, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde gezip bir bakmad\u0131lar m\u0131, kendilerinden \u00f6ncekilerin sonu nas\u0131l olmu\u015f? Halbuki onlar, bunlardan daha kuvvetliydiler. Ne g\u00f6klerde ve ne de yerde hi\u00e7bir \u015fey Allah'\u0131 aciz b\u0131rakamaz. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc o her \u015feyi bilendir, her \u015feye k\u00e2dir oland\u0131r."}, {"id": 583504, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 440, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3705, "text": "Bununla beraber Allah, insanlar\u0131 kazand\u0131klar\u0131 (g\u00fcnahlar) y\u00fcz\u00fcnden hemen yakalay\u0131verseydi, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde hi\u00e7bir canl\u0131 b\u0131rakmazd\u0131. Fakat onlar\u0131 belli bir s\u00fcreye kadar erteliyor. Nihayet ecelleri gelince gere\u011fini yapar. \u015e\u00fcphe yok ki Allah, kullar\u0131n\u0131 g\u00f6rmektedir."}]